file.name: videostreaming-component.openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Video Streaming Component
  description: Component
  version: 1.0.0
paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    SingleRoom:
      required:
        - room
      properties:
        room:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Room'
    Room:
      properties:
        room_id:
          type: string
        video_id:
          type: string
        audio_codec:
          type: string
        video_codec:
          type: string
        record:
          type: boolean
        room_server_fqdn:
          type: string
        participants_max:
          type: integer
        participants:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Participant'
    MultipleVideo:
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        videos:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Video'
      required:
        - total
        - videos
    SingleVideo:
      type: object
      properties:
        video:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Video'
      required:
        - video
    Video:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        id:
          type: string
        device_id:
          type: string
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        video_name:
          type: string
        video_description:
          type: string
        enabled:
          type: boolean
        created_at:
          type: string
        updated_at:
          type: string
      required:
        - id
        - resource_owner_id
        - created_at
        - updated_at
    Participant:
      type: object
      properties:
        participant_id:
          type: string
        token:
          type: string
        expires:
          type: integer
        target:
          type: integer
        used:
          type: integer
    PlayRequest:
      properties:
        fps:
          type: integer
        audio_codec:
          type: string
        video_codec:
          type: string
        record:
          type: boolean
        participants_max:
          type: integer
    VideoUpdateRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        video_name:
          type: string
        video_description:
          type: string
